ely incredible.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have worked so hard for this over the last year and I think you could see how much it meant to me when I crossed the line,' Hodgkinson told BBC Sport shortly after her incredible display.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9961610267101546, \"rank\": 0.00385376780160475, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.8947096588891464, \"rank\": 0.11672942698255179, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"her incredible display\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I can not believe I have finally done it and to do it here\\u2026 where better.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The audience was absolutely incredible, it felt like a home crowd in Paris.\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999597549, \"rank\": 4.0254330680459486e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The audience\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1338}, {\"ngram\": \"a home crowd\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am super, super happy.'\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson had to hold off a late challenge from both Ethiopia's Tsige Dguma and Kenya's Mary Moraa, who claimed silver and bronze respectively.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1429, \"end\": 1439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9961610267101546, \"rank\": 0.00385376780160475, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.972944395900142, \"rank\": 0.027751413729398076, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1510, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8675081203561267, \"rank\": 0.15272475711164865, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"score\": 0.8928347056180144, \"rank\": 0.06351929440009375, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a late challenge\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I feel like it could have been run any way.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to be up near the front, probably quicker than it was at the bell,' Hodgkinson explained when quizzed on her tactics.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9961610267101546, \"rank\": 0.00385376780160475, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"her tactics\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But doing the semi-finals and the final back-to-back, I feel like everyone was tired.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's tough!\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just wanted to save myself for that last 100m, I trusted myself.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that last 100m\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could feel Mary pushing me on the back straight but I kept my composure and got to the line first so I am super happy.'\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"score\": 0.8928347056180144, \"rank\": 