m me.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"the next four years\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not believe it.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have seen all the support from home, I have seen people messaging me and I appreciate everyone.\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the support\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2502}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I may not have got back to everyone yet but I will do!\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Honestly, it could not feel more amazing to have that support and I am just super happy I can bring it come for my team and everybody.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that support\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"my team\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not just me, my people know who they are.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my people\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a whole team effort so this is our gold medal.'\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a whole team effort\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"our gold medal\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases